PrecisRegulations Amending SCHEDULE A to the FOOD AND DRUGS ACT (1116 - LIVER DISEASE) by replacing the reference to "Liver Disease" on the list of disease conditions in that schedule with "Liver Disease (except Hepatitis)" in order to allow for the advertisement and promotion of hepatitis vaccines to the general public.
